title: DJ DSK live set - Madlib Medicine Show Chengdu
description:
For more mixes goto:
www.mixcloud.com/djdsk2

A 40 minute segment from my warm up set for Madlib's Medicine show (Madlib & Egon) in Chengdu, China. 22nd Feb 2013!

Big thanks to Dave , Andy and all the guys at MODE for putting on the event! Definitely was amazing to see Madlib and Egon in Chengdu, China!
